version_description:
This version has following new features:
• Sync pushed creatives to get recent changes from DoubleClick Studio.
• Tap the star next to a creative to add it to your favorites.
• Manually added previews now support non-JavaScript URLs.
• Bug fixes.

What's New
* Push creative previews to your device directly from DoubleClick Bid Manager.
* Preview with Millennial and MoPub SDKs.
* Use the new in-app console to view events for creatives pushed from Studio.
* Bug fixes.

* Manually add and preview video creatives using the IMA SDK
* Bug fixes

* Push creatives to the app directly from DCM.
* Built-in QR code scanner makes it easier to add creatives manually.
* Bug fixes

* Bug Fixes
* Removed support for Millennial and MoPub SDK's
